	t of bombastic music thatll take over the Shrek Rave! Its gonna be wild\, 
	whimsical\, and unforgettable as a crowd of ogre-loving beasts comes toget
	her to celebrate the iconic films music\, culture\, and all-out randomness
	. A crazy-viral night that soon took over cities outside of the U.S.\, peo
	ple have turned up dressed as Shrek\, Fiona\, Donkey\, and many more of it
	s quirky characters. Of course\, the highlight of the night is the dance f
	loor! All the hits such as Im a Believer\, Bad Reputation\, I Need a Hero\
	, Accidentally in Love\, and many more will have you dancing and letting i
	t all out. Pretty much a cultural marvel by now\, its clear why a huge dan
	ce floor is gonna pop up at The Crocodile for Shrek Rave on Saturday\, Mar
	ch 14th. Dont miss out by booking your tickets now!\nThis event is 21 and 
	over. Any ticket holder unable to present valid identification indicating 
	that they are at least 21 years of age will not be admitted to this event\
	, and will not be eligible for a refund. All sales are final. There are no
